### ============================================================
### Presale — Storefront + Cart + Checkout
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Storefront: anonymous (published products browse)
### Cart: authenticated; mutations require TrustedApiUser policy
### Checkout: authenticated + TrustedApiUser → initiate → confirm → orderId
###
### Full checkout flow:
###   1. Browse products      →  GET  /api/storefront/products  (anonymous)
###   2. Add to cart          →  POST /api/cart/items           (TrustedApiUser)
###   3. View cart            →  GET  /api/cart                 (authenticated)
###   4. Initiate checkout    →  POST /api/checkout/initiate    (TrustedApiUser, locks prices 15-min TTL)
###   5. Confirm order        →  POST /api/checkout/confirm     (TrustedApiUser)
###   6. Get order + payment  →  GET  /api/orders/{orderId}     (see sales-orders.http)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# STOREFRONT — public product browse (anonymous)
# ============================================================

### Browse published products — first page
# Expected: 200 OK  →  StorefrontProductListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
###

### Browse published products — search
# Expected: 200 OK  →  filtered list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?searchString=laptop&pageSize=5&pageNo=1
###

### Browse published products — next page
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?pageSize=5&pageNo=2
###

# ============================================================
# CART — GET requires Authorize; mutations require TrustedApiUser
# ============================================================

### Get current user's cart
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CartVm  |  404 if cart is empty/doesn't exist
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Add item to cart (or update quantity if already in cart)  [TrustedApiUser]
# Expected: 200 OK
# Max 5 units per line (MaxApiQuantityFilter); Web UI cap is 99
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "8e445865-a24d-4543-a6c6-9443d048cdb9",
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}
###

### Add another item  [TrustedApiUser]
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "replace-with-real-user-id",
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}
###

### Update quantity of existing cart item (same productId → overwrites)  [TrustedApiUser]
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "8e445865-a24d-4543-a6c6-9443d048cdb9",
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 5
}
###

### Remove single item from cart  [TrustedApiUser]
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Clear entire cart  [TrustedApiUser]
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get cart after clearing — should be empty/404
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

# ============================================================
# CHECKOUT — TrustedApiUser required
# Steps: initiate → confirm
#   1. POST /api/checkout/initiate  — lock prices into SoftReservations (15-min TTL)
#   2. POST /api/checkout/confirm   — place the order; returns { orderId }
#      Then: GET /api/orders/{orderId} to get paymentUrl (sales-orders.http)
# ============================================================

### Step 4 — Initiate checkout (lock prices + TTL)  [TrustedApiUser]
# Locks the current Catalog price for every cart item into a SoftReservation (15-min TTL).
# Re-calling refreshes prices and resets the TTL (idempotent).
# 200 OK         →  { "reservedCount": <int>, "unavailableProductIds": [] }
# 409 Conflict   →  all products unavailable / checkout already in progress
# 400 Bad Request → cart is empty
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Step 5 — Confirm order placement  [TrustedApiUser]
# Customer data is submitted directly from the form (may be pre-filled from AccountProfile).
# No server-side customer lookup is performed — the inline data is embedded in the order.
# 200 OK        →  { "orderId": <int> }
# 400 Bad Request  →  no active soft reservations (must re-initiate checkout)
# 409 Conflict     →  a product is no longer available in the requested quantity
# 422 Unprocessable Entity  →  order service returned a failure (e.g. invalid customer data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkout/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currencyId": 1,
  "customer": {
    "firstName": "Jan",
    "lastName": "Kowalski",
    "email": "jan.kowalski@example.com",
    "phoneNumber": "+48123456789",
    "isCompany": false,
    "companyName": null,
    "nip": null,
    "street": "ul. Testowa",
    "buildingNumber": "1",
    "flatNumber": null,
    "zipCode": "00-001",
    "city": "Warszawa",
    "country": "Poland"
  }
}
###
